PrecisORDER PROHIBITING ENTRY ON CERTAIN LANDS IN THE YUKON TERRITORY (1997-No.7, Nordenskiold Wetland Habitat Protection Area, Y.T.) - which prohibits, until August 31, 2000, the staking of mineral claims or prospecting for precious minerals on some 77.6 square kilometres of land situated on the Nordenskiold River.
